		<mj-section>
			<mj-column>
				<mj-image alt="Kage; February 2024." src="https://github.com/mjcampagna/mjml/blob/main/newsletters/202402/20240203-115518-mc-27090.jpg?raw=true" />
				<mj-text css-class="article">
					<p>Hi [Name,fallback=Friend],</p>
					<p>It's a big newsletter this month, with lots of links to external reading. But a lot has been happening. There is some doomerism here, but I have tried to maintain some optimism as well. I hope it lands.</p>
					<p>And I mention it below, but I think it important enough to say here at the top as well, <a href="https://www.404media.co/tumblr-and-wordpress-to-sell-users-data-to-train-ai-tools/" target="_blank">Tumblr and WordPress are selling users' data to train AI tools</a>. I know a lot of folks use WordPress for blogging; be sure to opt out in whatever way you can.</p>
					<p>But we are offering some advice below how to protect yourself and your site from AI bots, and I tried out the Apple Vision Pro! Read on for all this, and more!</p>
				</mj-text>        
			</mj-column>
